latestPosts.caption:
Really excited to share the recent experience of doing makeup for one of the most loved actors @rupaliganguly . Just yesterday, she appeared as the only female jury member at the first ever National Creators Award in Delhi. A fantastic recognition initiative by our honourable Prime Minister @narendramodi Sir. I feel humbled that she chose me to do her makeup for this prestigious event focused on encouraging the digital content creators. The fact that it took place on Women’s Day, makes it all the more special to see a strong woman like her taking the stage and spreading her elegance ❤️❤️
